className=\"text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\">\n                                        this sentence was generated by our 100m\n                                        tinylm for mathqa model and i found it\n                                        cool so here it is\n                                    </p>\n                                    <div className=\"absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500/0 via-violet-500/5 to-violet-500/0 animate-shimmer bg-[length:200%_100%] rounded-xl\" />\n                                </div>\n                            </TooltipContent>\n                        </Tooltip>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <span\n                        className=\"text-sm font-medium text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400\"\n                        suppressHydrationWarning\n                    >\n                        Â© {currentYear}\n                    </span>\n                </div>\n            </footer>\n        </TooltipProvider>\n    );\n}\n",
